Prepare monthly actual vs budget/forecast analysis and document the actual trends against the plan 
Other ad hoc analysis based on business needs 
 About You 
BA/BS degree in finance or accounting from a leading institution; MBA or Masters preferred 
5+ years of work experience in an FP&A role; with a majority of this at a SaaS, B2B tech startup, is a must have! 
Advanced proficiency in Excel and PowerPoint, including ability to develop financial models and presentations from scratch required 
Strong understanding of GAAP and Financial Statements required 
Strong financial acumen and strong planning, analytical, leadership and operations skills 
Extensive experience working directly with executives and senior business leaders 
Highly organized, self-starter and able to deal with ambiguity 
Comfortable working with global business partners across regions 
 Nice to Have 
Bonus points for experience with NetSuite, Salesforce, Bamboo, Lever 
Experience with planning systems such as Adaptive, Anaplan or Host Analysis 
Experience supporting GTM teams and revenue models 
